"COMBAT SENSE"

Adds a number of dice equal to its rating to the adept's combat pool.

^WSee Also: ABILITIES, COMBAT POOL^n

Category: ^gDETECTION^n
Duration: ^gSUSTAINED^n

This spell increases the combat pool of the target by half of the
successes made when casting up to a maximum of the force.

^WSee Also: CAST^n
